# Bubble sort
def bubble(arr):
 for i in range(len(arr)):
  for j in range(0, len(arr)-i-1):
   if arr[j]>arr[j+1]: arr[j],arr[j+1]=arr[j+1],arr[j]
a=[5,3,8]
bubble(a)
print(a)
```

 for i in range(len(arr)):
  for j in range(0, len(arr)-i-1):
   if arr[j]>arr[j+1]: arr[j],arr[j+1]=arr[j+1],arr[j]
a=[5,3,8]
bubble(a)
print(a)
```

# Cell 7413 — Topic: Sorting Algorithms
# Bubble sort
def bubble(arr):
 for i in range(len(arr)):
  for j in range(0, len(arr)-i-1):
   if arr[j]>arr[j+1]: arr[j],arr[j+1]=arr[j+1],arr[j]
a=[5,3,8]
bubble(a)
print(a)
